{"tid":1635072,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[2015區議會選舉] 0","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:47.000Z","uid":331459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1fcd151aa63a01ab04578dafa1988e68c2a173ae","tid":1635072,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"仲有7個星期就係2019年 區選(如果有)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候做一啲分析，作好準備。10月4至17號為提名期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年 區議會選舉 479席 [包括當然議員 27席]<br />\n27席當然議員為新界鄉事委員會主席 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XN83bm3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXN83bm3.png&h=abcb7fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2015年 區議會選舉 458席結果 <br />\n建制派 324席 [當然議員 27席].  70.7%<br />\n民主派 126席. 27.5%<br />\n其他 8席. 1.7%<br />\n<br />\n458席當中68席自動當選 [15.8%]，大多數人均屬於建制陣營. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzvdyC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzvdyC8.png&h=00c1d74c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}